*This event is split up into 2 parts - the Adventure Map, and your Base Camp.
*'''Adventure Map''' - explore the island and play minigames to get Adventure Coins, which can be traded for rewards in the shop.
**'''Open-Air Bath''': Placing your shipgirls in the Open-Air Bath allows them to recover Morale at a faster rate than normal.
**'''Random Event''': You may encounter 3 types of events while adventuring around Seabreeze Island. Story events can only be completed once. Minigames and random events will refresh daily.
**'''Minigames''': Click to play new minigame "Manjuu Mining Battle" and rerun minigames "Manjuu Misadventures" & "Manjuu Salvaging Crew".
**'''Garden''': Materials can be harvested every day from 0:00 on the second day after opening.
*'''Base Camp''' - use the resources you found on the island to expand your camp and craft items to receive rewards and open up new areas to explore.
**'''Event story''': Upgrade your Base Camp level to progress through the Uncharted Summer event story.
**'''Manjuu Papercraft''': Here you can create gifts for your shipgirls using the materials you've gathered and the items you've made at the Crafting Station. The shipgirls will reciprocate your gift and give you rewards such as materials and Adventure Coins.
**'''The Mission Board''': The Mission Board has list of missions you can complete, earning you Adventure Coins and other rewards for your efforts. You can also check the Records to see how far into the story you are and how much of the island you've explored. As you fill in the pages, you'll get hints showing you where to find hidden treasure chests on the Adventure Map.
